  "prompt": "Which is the best website or a portal to read Tamil literature?",
  "response": "There are several excellent websites and portals where you can read Tamil literature. Some popular options include:\n\n1. **Project Madurai** - A digital library dedicated to Tamil literature, offering numerous classical texts in Tamil for free.\n\n2. **Tamil Virtual University** - Provides a collection of various Tamil literary works and resources for learning Tamil.\n\n3. **TamilBooks.com** - Offers a selection of Tamil books and literature, including novels, poetry, and essays, which may be available for purchase or free download.\n\n4. **Archive.org** - While not exclusively for Tamil literature, you can find a variety of Tamil texts and literature available for free.\n\n5. **Koodal (koodal.com)** - A portal dedicated to Tamil literature, featuring works from contemporary and classical authors.\n\n6. **Goodreads** - While more of a general platform, it has a significant collection of Tamil books where you can discover and read user reviews on various Tamil literary works.\n\n7. **Apple Books and Google Play Books** - Both platforms have a wide selection of Tamil literature available for purchase or download.\n\nThese platforms can help you explore both classic and contemporary Tamil literary works.",
